<div>
<div>
<h2>
<a href="https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2024/12/after-decades-of-talk-seagate-seems-ready-to-actually-drop-the-hamr-hard-drives/">After decades of talk, Seagate seems ready to actually drop the HAMR hard drives</a>
</h2>
<p>
At least one gigantic cloud provider has signed off on the drives' viability.
</p>
